title: WATCH: Kaepernick hits water boy on head with errant pass
text:
WATCH: Kaepernick hits water boy on head with errant pass Sportsnaut 10 hrs ago Jesse Reed Colin Kaepernick had a rough start to the Thursday Night Football game in Week 7, and so did a water boy on San Francisco’s sideline after an errant pass from the quarterback hit him right in the back of the head.
AdChoices Here is a video of the throw and resulting body swerve after the high-powered throw jolted his noggin.
Kaepernick hit someone right in the head on this errant sideline pass. #SEAvsSF (h/t @TheCauldron ) https://t.co/ugBDYVJo1d
— Sportsnaut (@Sportsnaut) October 23, 2015 Kaepernick is going to need to improve on his accuracy if he has any hope of leading the 49ers to victory.
